b'\xe2\x80\x9cWe as a family have really tried to listen to the different views and have an understanding of what is going on outside of our own bubble in our homes.\xe2\x80\x9d

Eight panelists discuss parenting and how dismantling racial injustice starts at home. Moderated by Black Girls RUN! CEO Jay Ell Alexander, they shared how they talk about racism with their kids, ways they continually educate themselves as parents and how they create a diverse environment for their children. 

